From d543bd54f1906978c3ff0a6b4e660f4cf08c8adc Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Mihail Maksimov <miha5424@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 22 Jun 2025 16:54:15 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 107/194] arm64: dts: qcom: Introduce support for Xiaomi Mi Mix
 3

Xiaomi Mi Mix 3, codename perseus is mobile phone released in 2018.

Works great:
 - Storage,
 - Display,
 - GPU,
 - Flashlight,
 - Bluetooth,
 - Sensors (excluding hall sensor).

Audio is working, but for full testing and use requires alsa ucm
configuration and maybe additional work.

[David]
 - small adaptation to use upstream FTS driver (w/ modifications)

Signed-off-by: Mihail Maksimov <miha5424@gmail.com>
Co-developed-by: David Heidelberg <david@ixit.cz>
Signed-off-by: David Heidelberg <david@ixit.cz>
